WEBVTT

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:37.220
Tell me your doubts in detail.

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:40.560
He went to such great lengths

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.170
to make it look like the head

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:44.460
and body were completely separated,

00:01:44.759 --> 00:01:46.840
almost creating the effect of a bizarre car accident.

00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:48.440
Why didn't he leave the head?

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.600
But actually, even Lu Wei himself didn't know

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:54.200
whether he ran over a living person or a corpse.

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:55.380
If there was a head,

00:01:55.600 --> 00:01:56.860
once Lu Wei confessed,

00:01:57.039 --> 00:01:58.300
the police would think

00:01:58.360 --> 00:01:59.400
the facts were clear,

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:00.680
and the evidence was sufficient,

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:02.680
and close the case as a car accident.

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:04.050
Just like back then.

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:10.699
Back then is back then.

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:14.280
There's nothing suspicious about Master's case.

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.480
He was my Master too.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:17.860
What about now?

00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:20.250
Do you agree with my deduction?

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:21.920
Your deduction is valid.

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:24.820
So why is the head missing?

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:26.320
I suspect the killer

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:27.980
took the head away on purpose.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:33.640
To dump a body in such a remote place,

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:35.800
they must have used a vehicle.

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.160
But why

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:38.900
is there no trace left?

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:52.850
Captain Sun.

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:56.120
Look closely.

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:58.810
This tire track is narrow and shallow,

00:02:58.880 --> 00:03:01.000
and it's overlapping with a larger vehicle's track.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.920
It's indeed very easy to overlook.

00:03:02.920 --> 00:03:04.840
That means after dumping the body...

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:05.640
The killer

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:07.320
deliberately followed the tracks of large trucks.

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:09.640
Once the large trucks started moving frequently,

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:10.920
they would easily cover up

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:11.720
the tire marks

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:12.620
he left behind.

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:14.160
Because there are cameras on the highway,

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:15.520
he didn't dare to take it.

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:17.850
He had to return to the city via dirt roads.

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:20.880
So,

00:03:21.480 --> 00:03:22.440
we can expand our scope

00:03:22.440 --> 00:03:24.570
and check the ring road surveillance.

00:03:42.079 --> 00:03:42.610
Found it.

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:45.920
This one

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:47.400
at 11:47

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:49.920
suddenly appeared on West Huancheng Road.

00:03:52.320 --> 00:03:52.920
This car

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:55.440
was last seen on the traffic camera outside Ziming Gardens

00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:56.480
at 12:24.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.560
The owner is Kong Jiao.

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:01.240
She lives in Building 3, Apartment 8-A, Ziming Gardens.

00:04:01.240 --> 00:04:02.040
Let's split up.

00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:03.280
Mr. Yan and I will go upstairs.

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:04.320
Lin Xiao, Jia Peng,

00:04:04.320 --> 00:04:06.520
you guys check the underground garage.

00:04:21.200 --> 00:04:22.000
8-A.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:31.360
Knock, knock, knock.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:32.440
Is there a time bomb

00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:34.080
planted in this house?

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.400
Every few days,

00:04:35.400 --> 00:04:37.530
a bunch of people come making a racket.

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:38.360
I'm telling you,

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:39.320
if you keep this up,

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:40.760
I'll call the police.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:43.920
Hello, ma'am.

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:45.240
We are the police.

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:48.159
Oh,

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:49.760
officers.

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:51.760
You should have told me earlier.

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:52.480
Hey.

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:54.800
The couple in that room,

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.400
did they do something wrong?

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:57.080
Oh,

00:04:57.080 --> 00:04:59.840
I always felt there was something wrong with that guy.

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:00.360
Ma'am,

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.080
tell us,

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:02.490
what was wrong with him?

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:04.040
That guy

00:05:04.520 --> 00:05:06.240
had no manners.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:09.800
He'd always make a lot of noise coming back from the night shift,

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:12.160
and he was always covered in rust scraps.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:14.680
He got it on my bedsheets a few times.

00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:15.320
Rust?

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:16.600
Ah, I remember.

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:17.640
One time,

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:19.160
he dropped a screwdriver

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:21.480
this thick and this long.

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:23.140
He picked it up and ran off.

00:05:23.320 --> 00:05:25.280
Was the rust on him reddish-brown

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:26.210
or bluish-gray?

00:05:26.520 --> 00:05:27.080
Well,

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:28.400
it wasn't really red,

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:29.260
nor was it gray.

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:30.440
Anyway, it was like

00:05:30.440 --> 00:05:31.960
the color of a blood scab.

00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:34.600
Red iron ore slag

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:36.480
mixed with the color of metal oxide.

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:40.480
It matches the corrosion characteristics of illegal mining transport vehicles.

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:41.000
Ma'am,

00:05:41.080 --> 00:05:41.920
tell us more.

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:43.520
How was the couple's

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:44.850
relationship usually?

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:46.600
Oh, I remember now.

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:47.640
Last month,

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:49.000
I heard outside

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:50.200
some crashing noises.

00:05:50.200 --> 00:05:52.400
I looked out through the peephole.

00:05:52.840 --> 00:05:53.800
I saw the woman

00:05:53.960 --> 00:05:55.800
run out, holding her shoulder.

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:57.159
The man

00:05:57.240 --> 00:05:59.200
took an iron bar this long,

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:00.320
pointed at her and said,

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:01.320
'If you run again,

00:06:01.520 --> 00:06:02.780
I'll break your legs.'

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:03.640
Tell me,

00:06:03.760 --> 00:06:05.440
is that something a human would say?

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:06.480
What's the man's name?

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:06.960
Oh,

00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:08.720
I have no idea about that.

00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:11.200
That's all.

00:06:11.200 --> 00:06:12.120
Thank you, ma'am.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:12.520
Thank you.

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:13.000
Okay.

00:06:30.280 --> 00:06:31.210
Hello, manager.

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:33.040
Please open the door to room 8-A.

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:34.890
Here is the search warrant.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:20.520
Yan.

00:07:23.320 --> 00:07:24.400
Kong Jiao must be

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:26.200
living with another man.

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:28.160
All the daily necessities

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:29.220
are for two people.

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:32.180
Underwear.

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:33.159
Money.

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:34.600
Her ID is here.

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:36.400
None of her basic necessities

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:37.130
are missing.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:41.840
But the surveillance footage captured

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:43.120
Kong Jiao's car.

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:44.170
Theoretically,

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:45.210
she is a suspect.

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:47.400
Judging by how tidy her house is,

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:49.800
it doesn't seem like she fled after a crime.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:52.200
Kong Jiao probably isn't the murderer.

00:07:54.680 --> 00:07:56.040
Could the murderer be

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:57.300
the man who abused her?

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.840
Maybe he killed someone,

00:07:58.840 --> 00:07:59.840
used her car

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:01.180
to move the victim.

00:08:02.640 --> 00:08:04.100
The murderer was ruthless

00:08:04.520 --> 00:08:06.160
and meticulously planned it.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:08.360
The execution of the plan was very calm.

00:08:08.400 --> 00:08:09.200
Kong Jiao

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:12.220
might have been taken away by the killer.

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:20.280
Jiang E: 18238

00:08:21.920 --> 00:08:22.480
Lin Xiao.

00:08:39.799 --> 00:08:40.360
Captain Sun.

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:43.360
Kong Jiao's car was found in the underground parking.

00:08:45.560 --> 00:08:46.760
We'll be right there.

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:24.320
Lin Xiao,

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:25.800
put it away.

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:45.610
Captain Sun.

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:56.120
What is this?

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:57.900
Could it be left by the killer?

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:02.360
Hey.